		<div>
			<div class="header">Provider security guardrails</div>
			<div>The following rules are enforced in the sender and receiver side. Any detected abuse by the sender or receiver immediately raises a provider dispute as defined in the <a href="https://github.com/bringyour/product/whitepaper.md" target="_blank">whitepaper</a>.</div>
