						<td class="amount">No access to non-public IPv4 and IPv6 subnets as defined by RFC 1918, RFC 4193, and other related RFCs. Only public addresses are allowed to be routed.</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td class="item"><img src="res/images/superfast.svg" alt="bullet"></td>
						<td class="amount">Only end-to-end TLS and dTLS encrypted traffic is allowed. Unencypted traffic will not pass through a provider.</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
